description: These simple egg muffins are the perfect grab and go breakfast, make a batch at the start of the week.
keywords: Savoury muffin,Pescatarian,Seafood free,Gluten free,Tree nut free,Egg,Sesame free,Savoury Muffins,Halal,Soy free,Wheat free,Vegetarian,Spinach,Peanut free
name: Feta, Spinach & Herb Egg Muffins Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Pre-heat the oven to 180°C/160°C fan-forced. Grease a six cup muffin tray with a small amount of oil.
Beat the eggs in a large bowl, add the spinach, spring onions and chopped herbs and mix well. Crumble over the feta and stir to combine.
Season with salt and pepper and use a ladle to fill each cup in the muffin tray.
Bake until golden, puffed up and bubbling, 20-25 minutes. These can be served warm or stored in the fridge and eaten cold.
